flowchart LR
  GH[GitHub Actions / local CI] --> WIF[Workload Identity Federation]
  WIF --> Build[Cloud Build]
  Build --> AR[Artifact Registry]
  AR --> CR[Cloud Run Services]
  CR --> SQL[(Cloud SQL PG16)]
  CR --> SM[Secret Manager]
  PipelineJob[Cloud Run Jobs] --> SQL
  PipelineJob --> BQ[(BigQuery measurement)]
  Scheduler[Cloud Scheduler] --> PipelineJob
  CR --> GCS[(GCS uploads/raw)]
  Logs[Cloud Logging/Monitoring] --- CR
  Logs --- PipelineJob

